<br>
You see, my brother, Sekali, and I were orphaned at an early age, and I was put in charge of bringing him up. Sekali was not the brightest torch on the wall and was prone to wandering, so taking care of him was a full-time task.<br>
However, we were quite poor, so when I was given the chance to be an apprentice and learn the skills of an enchanter (and jewelsmith), I jumped at the opportunity. Soon after I started my schooling my brother, unknown to me, hopped on the boat to Antonica and was reportedly captured by the Tier'Dal, presumably to be sold into slavery. The guilt I feel at letting him fall into their foul clutches is unbearable. It has become my life's work to find and rescue him. <br>
<br>
I headed to Antonica before my early training was complete(level 5) to look for him. I spent a lot of time prowling through in dark elf form through the dank, dark streets of Neriak, searching for clues to his whereabouts. When my search turned up nothing, I turned my frustrations on the dark elf guards, killing them over and over near the entrance to Lavastorm. The Neriak citizens now hate me on site, regardless of my disguise, so I doubt I'll ever enter that horrible city again. <br>
<br>
My training has continued at a slow pace, mostly because I am constantly wandering, hoping to hear word of my brother. I'm now in my 23rd season and still have heard nothing of Sekali, though I have donned the dark elf disguise many times and joined their ranks for adventuring and to learn their snarling, gutteral language. There have been many awkward moments after my disguise has faded while grouping with their kind, but no matter. I remain steadfast in my quest, and will continue to hunt for word of him.<br>
<br>
If you see a high elf lad, with white hair and dark eyes, who answers to the name of Sekali, give him my love, and tell him I am coming for him...<br>
<br>
Halus <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uroninsenshi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RoninSenshi</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia</span><br>  Posts: 235<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/14/02 10:18:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1109.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I'm not a jerk, I just play one in FV</span><hr size=1> ((No, I'm the fool. Misread post, Sorry ^_^. Have fun with it, and.)) DON'T ASSIST NEUTRALS..<br>
